# nettup.no

Marketing website for Nettup, a web development agency based in Norway.

## Stack

| Layer        | Technology                          |
| ------------ | ----------------------------------- |
| Framework    | Astro 5 (static output)             |
| Styling      | Tailwind CSS 4                      |
| Interactivity| React 19 islands + Framer Motion 12 |
| Deployment   | Vercel                              |
| Analytics    | Plausible (cookieless, GDPR)        |
| Testing      | Vitest                              |

## Architecture

Astro handles static rendering, layout, and SEO. React islands hydrate only where interactivity is required (forms, chat widget, animations). Three animation tiers: CSS transitions, IntersectionObserver reveals, and Framer Motion sequences.

```
src/
  components/
    islands/       React components (ChatWidget, HeroIsland, PrisKalkulator, ...)
    sections/      Shared Astro sections (CTA, Testimonials, ...)
    ui/            Primitives (Button, Card, Section, SectionHeader)
    layout/        Footer, FloatingNav
  config/          Content and data (services, pricing, locations, brand tokens)
  content/blogg/   Astro Content Collection (blog articles)
  layouts/         BaseLayout.astro
  lib/             Utilities, calculation engine, animation helpers
  pages/           Route tree (14 pages)
  scripts/blog/    Automated blog generation pipeline
  styles/          global.css (animation keyframes, accessibility)
```

## Development

```bash
npm install
npm run dev          # localhost:4321
npm run build        # Production build
npm run preview      # Preview production build
npm run test         # Run tests
npm run lint         # ESLint
npm run format       # Prettier
```

## Pages

| Route                    | Purpose                         |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------------- |
| `/`                      | Homepage                        |
| `/tjenester`             | Service catalog                 |
| `/tjenester/nettside`    | Website service detail          |
| `/tjenester/nettbutikk`  | E-commerce service detail       |
| `/tjenester/landingsside`| Landing page service detail     |
| `/om-oss`                | About the agency                |
| `/prosjekter`            | Portfolio                       |
| `/prosjekter/[slug]`     | Case study pages                |
| `/kontakt`               | Contact form                    |
| `/priskalkulator`        | Pricing wizard                  |
| `/blogg`                 | Blog index                      |
| `/blogg/[slug]`          | Blog articles                   |
| `/nettside-for-bedrift`  | B2B landing page                |
| `/personvern`            | Privacy policy                  |

## Configuration

All content data lives in `src/config/`:

- **services.ts** -- service definitions, pricing, launch discounts
- **pricing.ts** -- package tiers (Enkel, Standard, Premium)
- **locations.ts** -- Norwegian cities for geo-targeting
- **brand.ts** -- design tokens (colors, fonts, spacing, animation timing)
- **projects.ts** -- portfolio entries
- **testimonials.ts** -- social proof
- **chatbot.ts** -- AI chat widget configuration

## Key Conventions

- All user-facing content is in Norwegian (bokmal)
- Mobile-first design (375px baseline)
- `prefers-reduced-motion` respected across all animation tiers
- First section on any page uses `pt-32 md:pt-40` to clear the fixed navbar
- Forms submit to Formspree (`xnjnzybj`)
